page.title: 19My Day
page.content: I wake up at about 7 am & read until 7:45.I get dressed and washed & go down to breakfast.After breakfast I watch T.V. before going to school.I always call at my nanas halfway to school.When I get to school I play with my friends.When the bell goes we go into assembly in the hall.After we come out we usually do maths or English or a special topic.We have a playtime at 10:35 and we play a game. Playtime finishes at 10:55 & we go back into school.Sometimes we have a telivision or radio programme.At dinnertime I go home for dinner.I get back to school at 12:35.After playtime which finishes at 1:15 we do work again.There is another playtime at 2:30 and that finishes at about 2:55. We go home at 3:55 then I have my tea straight away.I usually watch TV for an hour then I go out to play.
